==================================================

Refactor the generator engine so it no longer only reads fixed phases.

Instead the generator must:

1. resolve patient profile
2. select protocol blueprint
3. apply age / sex / duration / tempo rules
4. build final phase plan
5. generate medication schedule
6. generate monitoring schedule
7. run clinical validation
8. generate artifacts

